# ⚠️  This file is the TEMPLATE. It is git-tracked.
# ⚠️  DO NOT put real secrets here. Copy to `.env` (gitignored) instead.
#
# Setup:
#   cp server/.env.example server/.env     (or copy in Explorer)
#   Then edit server/.env with the values below.

# NetEase Cloud Music — required to resolve VIP-locked songs.
# How to fetch:
#   1. Open https://music.163.com/ in your browser, log in.
#   2. F12 -> Application tab -> Cookies -> https://music.163.com
#   3. Copy the value of MUSIC_U
#   4. In server/.env  paste as: NCM_COOKIE=MUSIC_U=<the long value>
#
# A single MUSIC_U cookie is enough; you don't need __csrf or others.
# This token is your account auth — DO NOT commit, share, or paste in chats.
# If it leaks, log out of music.163.com to invalidate the token, then re-login
# to get a new one.
NCM_COOKIE=
